data.description: Your dream home awaits! Beautiful 2 story brick and hardy home has so much to offer. With an upstairs and downstairs suite, this home can suite your needs. This stunner home has a foyer that is vaulted to the 2nd floor, 4 bedrooms, bonus room, 3.5 bathrooms, downstairs office, formal dining room with wainscoting, large eat-in kitchen with granite counters tops, kitchen island, spacious master bath and large walk-in closets. You'll enjoy spending time in this beautiful, secluded and fenced in back yard, which also has a dog run. A full irrigation system is in place, double garage with storage space and completely new 2nd story HVAC system.
